metadata.name: Dinner for two or a dumpling fight.
metadata.description:
The panda sitting next to them laughs and secretly thinks, "Maybe I can help them divide the dumplings equally. After all, I'm a great mediator!" But she realizes that would be too easy and uninteresting, and decides to just watch this fight. In the end, the one who pounces on the last dumpling faster and more deftly wins!
And who got the dumpling, you decide for yourself...
